---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Privacy Policy | Ibiza Cool Party',
  description: 'Privacy policy for ibizacoolparty.com — how we handle your data.',
  noindex: true,
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 prose prose-invert">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: May 2025</em></p>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      Ibiza Cool Party ("we", "us", or "our") operates the website ibizacoolparty.com. This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email address (if you subscribe to our newsletter)</li>
      <li>Usage data (pages visited, time on site) via analytics</li>
      <li>Cookies for site functionality and affiliate tracking</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To send you our newsletter (only if you opt in)</li>
      <li>To improve our website and content</li>
      <li>To track affiliate referrals</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>
      We use third-party services that may collect information. These include our affiliate partners (GetYourGuide, Viator, Welcome Pickups) and analytics services.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Our site uses cookies to improve your experience and for affiliate tracking purposes. You can control cookie settings in your browser.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>
      You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. Contact us at hola@ibizacoolparty.com for any requests.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For any privacy-related questions, email us at: <a href="mailto:hola@ibizacoolparty.com">hola@ibizacoolparty.com</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
